title: 6 Chess Books (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 6 Chess Books. Out if these, Tournament Chess - Volume 20 is my scan & 3 others are converted from DJVU:

1. Accelerated Dragons by Jeremy Silman and John Donaldson
2. How to Play the Sicilian Defence by DAVID LEVY. KEVIN O'CONNELL
3. Pandolfini's Endgame Course - Basic Endgame Concepts Explained by America's Leading Chess Teacher 
4. The Art of Planning in Chess - Move by Move by Neil McDonald
5. The Art of Positional Play by Samuel Reshevsky
6. Tournament Chess - Volume 20 (magazine)
